聆听灵魂偶像 Al Green 衷心翻唱 REM 的《Everybody Hurts》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-soul-icon-al-greens-heartfelt-cover-of-rem-everybody-hurts-3814295?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-灵魂图标阿尔·格林衷心封面雷姆每个人都受伤了Laura MolloyWed, 20 Nov 2024 09:40:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeIndieSoul https://www.nme.com/?p=3814295 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我真的能感受到这首歌的沉重，我想给它注入一点希望和光明”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-soul-icon-al-greens-heartfelt-cover-of-rem-everybody-hurts-3814295">聆听灵魂偶像 Al Green 对 REM 歌曲《Everybody Hurts》的衷心翻唱，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Al-Green.-CREDIT_-David-Raccuglia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/al-green">艾尔·格林牧师 (Reverand Al Green)</a>分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/r-e-m">REM</a>歌曲《Everybody Hurts》的深情翻唱。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/rem-monster-interview-michael-stipe-mike-mills-cobain-phoenix-video-2562624"><b><i>NME</i></b><b>遇见 REM：“我们需要昂首阔步——大声而原始”</b></a></li></ul><p>这位美国歌手、词曲作者、牧师和唱片制作人近年来发行了一些翻唱作品。 2020 年，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hear-al-greens-cover-of-before-the-next-teardrop-falls-his-first-new-recording-in-a-decade-2843334">分享了 Freddy Fender 的《Before the Next Teardrop Falls》的版本</a>，随后在 2023 年翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lou-reed">Lou Reed</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/al-green-returns-with-cover-of-lou-reeds-perfect-day-tour-dates-listen-buy-tickets-3486750">《Perfect Day》</a> 。</p><p>现在，他演绎了 REM 1992 年第八张录音室专辑《Automatic for the People》中的开创性热门歌曲。格林的版本偏离了原版的阴郁色调，为歌曲引入了更乐观的能量。</p><p> “当我们在录音室录制《Everybody Hurts》时，”他说，“我真的能感受到这首歌的沉重，我想给它注入一点希望和光明。总有光明的存在，可以冲破那些黑暗的时光。”</p><p>它也获得了 REM 的批准。主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">迈克尔·斯蒂普（Michael Stipe）</a>为封面开了绿灯，他说：“代表整个乐队发言——我们感到无比荣幸、受宠若惊、谦卑不已。这对我们来说是一个史诗般的时刻。”</p><p>看看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="艾尔·格林 - 每个人都受伤（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UEwPIfk6LpQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Everybody Hurts》是 REM 最著名的热门歌曲之一，自发行以来就已融入流行文化。 2019 年，该团体 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rem-respond-to-trump-meme-everybody-hurts-2448756-2448756">对特朗普在一个模因中使用他们的歌曲《Everybody Hurts》做出了反应</a>，该模因将他的国情咨文定位为针对包括亚历山大·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯和伯尼·桑德斯在内的情绪低落的政客。</p><p>最近，REM <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/r-e-m-share-new-lyric-video-for-i-believe-to-encourage-people-to-vote-in-us-election-3808077">分享了他们 1986 年热门单曲“I Believe”的新歌词视频</a>，鼓励人们在最近的美国大选中投票。在此之前，发行了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/r-e-m-share-we-are-hope-despite-the-times-compilation-to-mark-national-voter-registration-day-3794616">纪念全国选民登记日的数字歌曲合辑《We Are Hope Without The Times》</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="快速眼动回顾他们的遗产和 25 年的《Monster》" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zG8MpHbLIK8?start=1295&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，去年 12 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-stipe-offers-update-on-his-debut-solo-album-i-have-a-deadline-now-3552487">斯蒂普透露，由于家庭紧急情况、搬家和新冠疫情，他的首张个人专辑被推迟了 12 个月，但他仍在制作首张个人专辑</a>。</p><p>他还表示，他遭受了“可怕”的症状，但补充说，在与母亲见面后，他现在感到了分娩的压力。 “我现在有一个最后期限，”他说。 “我可以继续为这张唱片工作十年，让我的不安全感占据上风。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-soul-icon-al-greens-heartfelt-cover-of-rem-everybody-hurts-3814295">聆听灵魂偶像 Al Green 对 REM 歌曲《Everybody Hurts》的衷心翻唱，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
