韩国劳动部驳回 NewJeans 职场欺凌指控https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-by-koreas-labour-ministry-3814273?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=newjeans-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-韩国劳动部Carmen ChinWed, 20 Nov 2024 08:53:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3814273 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新牛仔裤汉尼工作场所欺凌指控被劳工部驳回" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据国家现行劳动法，偶像不属于雇员</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-by-koreas-labour-ministry-3814273">韩国劳动部驳回 NewJeans 工作场所欺凌指控的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新牛仔裤汉尼工作场所欺凌指控被劳工部驳回" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/newjeans-hanni-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-labour-minidstry-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>韩国雇佣劳动部驳回了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">NewJeans</a>关于工作场所骚扰的指控。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ador-hybe-feud-timeline-story-3754759">HYBE-ADOR 不和：事件的全面时间表</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<em><a href="https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20241120002900315?section=culture/k-pop">韩联社</a>报道，今天（11 月 20 日），该部宣布结束对 NewJeans 粉丝于 9 月中旬代表该乐队提出的工作场所欺凌指控的调查。</em>该案被驳回，因为根据该国现行劳动法，韩国流行偶像在法律上不被归类为雇员。</p><p>请愿书称，成员 Hanni 尤其在她的品牌 ADOR 的母公司 HYBE 内遭受工作场所欺凌。汉尼本人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-hanni-tearfully-testifies-workplace-harassment-hybe-3803060">在 10 月 15 日的国民议会会议</a>上作证时也提出了类似的主张。 “我开始意识到这不仅仅是一种感觉。老实说，我确信公司讨厌我们，”她当时说道。</p><p>该部解释说，她不符合雇员资格源于“汉尼签署的管理合同的内容和性质”。相反，韩国政府将艺人归类为“特殊实体”，而不是雇主与雇员关系中的雇员，因为他们根据带有管理标签的独家、基于佣金的合同进行运营。</p><p> NewJeans 的工作场所骚扰指控被驳回，大约一周前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-threaten-leave-ador-contract-breaches-not-rectified-3812562">据报道，该组织向 ADOR 发出警告，称如果“严重违反合同”问题得不到解决，将取消他们的合同</a>。</p><p>虽然该组织的要求细节没有具体说明，但他们此前在 9 月份举行了一次出人意料的直播<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-call-for-min-hee-jin-reinstated-ador-ceo-surprise-youtube-livestream-3792926">，呼吁恢复 Min</a>担任 ADOR 首席执行官的职务。两周后，该机构<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ador-reject-newjeans-request-reppaoint-min-hee-jin-ceo-3796835">拒绝了他们的请求</a>。</p><p>今天（11月20日），ADOR前首席执行官闵熙珍宣布辞去公司董事会职务。在 Min 公开声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/min-hee-jin-claims-hybe-ador-offer-continue-producing-newjeans-unreasonable-3788999">辞职不是她的选择</a>后，她最终于 9 月下旬<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ador-reject-newjeans-request-reppaoint-min-hee-jin-ceo-3796835">恢复担任 ADOR 董事会内部董事</a>。</p><p>敏在声明中表示，她打算“对 HYBE 及其关联公司实施的众多非法活动一一采取必要的法律行动”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-workplace-bullying-claims-dismissed-by-koreas-labour-ministry-3814273">韩国劳动部驳回 NewJeans 工作场所欺凌指控的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
